Secretary-General on the situation of human rights in Haiti. 
</p>
<p>37. At the same meeting, Mr. Louis Joinet, independent expert appointed by the 
Secretary-General on the situation of human rights in Haiti, made a statement. 
</p>
<p>38. During the ensuing discussion, the following made statements: 
