Mexico, Netherlands, Nicaragua, Nigeria, Pakistan (on behalf of the Organization of the Islamic 
Conference), Peru, Philippines, Portugal<b>13</b> (on behalf of the European Union), Republic of 
Korea, Russian Federation, South Africa, Sri Lanka and Switzerland; 
</p>
